Titolo: Darkwood

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Darkwood is a top-down survival horror video game developed by Acid Wizard Studio. The game was first released through Steam Early Access on July 24, 2014, Eventually becoming a full game release on August 17, 2017 for Microsoft Windows, macOS, SteamOS and Ubuntu. The game takes place in a mysterious dark forest somewhere in Polish People's Republic or somewhere else in the territory of the Soviet Bloc, where the main characters have been trapped for an unknown amount of time. On March 20, 2019, a Nintendo Switch version was announced during the Nindies Nintendo Direct and was released on May 16, 2019. The game was also ported and released for the PlayStation 4 on May 14, 2019, and for Xbox One on May 16, under the publisher Crunching Koalas.